title: The Phantom Fill Pack
description:
This torrent contains comics which help to fill out the recent Phantom mega torrent by Rishab.  I tried to match directory structure with Rishab as these files supplement his existing torrent.

As is obvious from the gaps in issue numbers, there are still quite a few Phantom books left to scan.  And there is certainly scanned Phantom material still untorrented.  While working on this torrent I came across an exhuastive (9GB) collection of the newspaper strips.  I don&#039;t have this yet myself, so if some kind soul ...

The Phantom has been around for more than 70 years (he predates Superman) and is popular all over the world.  The wikipedia article (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Phantom) is extensive.
